            .single-comments__item 
                .single-comments__user 
                    img.single-comments__avatar(src="/assets/images/single-item/user-2.png", alt="user-avatar") 
                    strong.single-comments__fullname Игорь Зубарев 
                p.single-comments__descr I really appreciate the insights and perspective shared in this article. It's definitely given me something to think about and has helped me see things from a different angle. Thank you for writing and sharing!
        a.single-comments__loadmore(href="#!") Загрузить еще 

